, "bbox": [1131.1, 452.0, 1183.2, 467.6]}, {"text": "29,953", "bbox": [1233.2, 452.0, 1285.3, 467.6]}, {"text": "16.7", "bbox": [1329.9, 452.0, 1364.5, 467.6]}, {"text": "7.3", "bbox": [1420.5, 452.0, 1443.6, 467.6]}, {"text": "6.7", "bbox": [1498.8, 452.0, 1520.5, 467.6]}, {"text": "Total International", "bbox": [860.1, 477.0, 1010.1, 492.6]}, {"text": "205,323", "bbox": [1122.4, 477.0, 1183.2, 492.6]}, {"text": "180,053", "bbox": [1224.7, 477.0, 1285.3, 492.6]}, {"text": "14.0", "bbox": [1330.3, 477.0, 1364.5, 492.6]}, {"text": "43.1", "bbox": [1408.9, 477.0, 1443.6, 492.6]}, {"text": "40.0", "bbox": [1490.1, 477.0, 1520.5, 492.6]}, {"text": "North America", "bbox": [860.1, 502.0, 972.2, 517.6]}, {"text": "270,288", "bbox": [1122.4, 502.0, 1183.2, 517.6]}, {"text": "269,955", "bbox": [1224.5, 502.0, 1285.3, 517.6]}, {"text": "0.1", "bbox": [1338.4, 502.0, 1364.5, 517.6]}, {"text": "56.9", "bbox": [1408.9, 502.0, 1443.6, 517.6]}, {"text": "60.0", "bbox": [1490.1, 502.0, 1520.5, 517.6]}, {"text": "Total sales", "bbox": [860.1, 527.0, 953.6, 542.6]}, {"text": "$475,611", "bbox": [1115.8, 527.0, 1183.2, 542.6]}, {"text": "$450,008", "bbox": [1215.2, 527.0, 1285.3, 542.6]}, {"text": "5.7", "bbox": [1338.4, 527.0, 1364.5, 542.6]}, {"text": "100.0", "bbox": [1400.4, 527.0, 1443.6, 542.6]}, {"text": "100.0", "bbox": [1481.7, 527.0, 1520.5, 542.6]}, {"text": "During 2002 and 2001, despite an economic downturn, Zebra implemented a", "bbox": [860.1, 584.5, 1486.3, 601.1]}, {"text": "growth strategy including:", "bbox": [860.1, 613.6, 1076.0, 630.3]}, {"text": "•  New Product Introductions—During 2002, Zebra spent $29 million on new prod-", "bbox": [860.1, 672.0, 1525.3, 688.6]}, {"text": "uct development activities, for salaries, benefits, consulting and legal services,", "bbox": [871.1, 701.1, 1517.8, 717.8]}, {"text": "market research, and related activities. Fourteen new products or derivative", "bbox": [871.1, 730.3, 1493.7, 747.0]}, {"text": "products were introduced during 2002, compared to 11 new products introduced", "bbox": [871.1, 759.5, 1532.2, 776.1]}, {"text": "during 2001.  Additionally, products introduced within the 18-month period ended", "bbox": [871.1, 788.6, 1541.0, 805.3]}, {"text": "December 31, 2002, represented 22% of printer sales for 2002.", "bbox": [871.1, 817.8, 1375.5, 834.5]}, {"text": "•  Expanded International Coverage—We opened six new sales offices during", "bbox": [860.1, 847.0, 1490.2, 863.6]}, {"text": "late 2001 through 2002, including Poland, Dubai, Russia, Australia, Brazil, and", "bbox": [871.1, 876.1, 1504.6, 892.8]}, {"text": "Argentina. We believe international regions, particularly Asia-Pacific, Latin", "bbox": [871.1, 905.3, 1482.0, 922.0]}, {"text": "America and Eastern Europe, hold significant growth potential.", "bbox": [871.1, 934.5, 1383.9, 951.1]}, {"text": "•  New sales and marketing programs—We organized sales and marketing efforts", "bbox": [860.1, 963.6, 1523.4, 980.3]}, {"text": "to support a sales strategy that demonstrates the business benefits associated", "bbox": [871.1, 992.8, 1516.8, 1009.5]}, {"text": "with implementing bar code labeling and specialty printing solutions.", "bbox": [871.1, 1022.0, 1436.5, 1038.6]}, {"text": "In North America, we recorded positive sales growth in the second, third and", "bbox": [860.1, 1080.3, 1492.6, 1097.0]}, {"text": "fourth quarters of 2002, compared with the corresponding periods of 2001. Overall,", "bbox": [860.1, 1109.5, 1541.4, 1126.1]}, {"text": "however, the slow U.S. economy continued to limit sales growth of bar code label", "bbox": [860.1, 1138.6, 1530.2, 1155.3]}, {"text": "and receipt printers to rates below our historical average.", "bbox": [860.1, 1167.8, 1332.4, 1184.5]}]}